                <Viewbox Grid.ColumnSpan="7" Grid.RowSpan="4" Grid.Row="6" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" >
                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="WrapWholeWords" Margin="50" Foreground="AliceBlue" FontFamily="Harrington"
                                VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Width="500" FontSize="40"
                          Text="How to play?&#x0a;
In this game you will use only two button in your keyboard: the up and down arrows.
To start the game you will need to press the right arrow key.
Your goal is to reach to the end of each level. If you lose all of your four warriors, you will lose.
In the way you will find and fight monsters. The fight will be done automatically when you touch the monster.  
You can jump between land logs an above monsters using the 'Up' arrow.
You can fall from land logs using long press on the 'Down' arrow.
Above each character you will see its remaining lives.
The stronger the monster you kill, the more money you get.
Use this money to improve your warriors!                              
&#x0a;&#x0a;
GOOD LUCK!!!!!!!!!!
                               ">
                    </TextBlock>
                </Viewbox>

